OL,5,Cin cars'
OL,7,FThe AA said it welcomed the increased
OL,8,Fuse of AI cameras which can detect
OL,9,Fmore offences beyond speeding, but
OL,10,Fwarned roads policing cannot be
OL,11,Fcarried out by cameras alone.
OL,13,FAbout nine out of 10 (91%) of its
OL,14,Fmembers surveyed said more traffic
OL,15,Fpolice would make communities safer.
OL,17,FLabour's general election manifesto
OL,18,Fincluded a pledge to recruit
OL,19,F"thousands" of new police officers to
OL,20,Ftackle neighbourhood crime.
