OL,7,F"The Neighbourhood Policing Guarantee
OL,8,Fwill provide a more visible police
OL,9,Fpresence and give every community a
OL,10,Fnamed local officer, alongside
OL,11,Fthousands more officers going into
OL,12,Fneighbourhood policing roles.
OL,14,F"Under the joint Roads Policing
OL,15,FReview, we are collaborating on a
OL,16,Frange of pilots which will test
OL,17,Fimprovements to roads policing
OL,18,Fcapabilities."
